* [name_utils::OpName(const string& dataset_type)](https://github.com/tensorflow/tensorflow/blob/master/tensorflow/core/kernels/data/name_utils.h#L58) will return something like `MapDataset`
* `DatasetParams::op_name()` return the dataset type (e.g. `Map`).

